│ ### Tool Call Format ###                                                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                                           │
│ When using a tool, return a JSON object strictly following below format:                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                                           │
│ <tool_call>                                                                                                                                               │
│ {                                                                                                                                                         │
│   "name": <tool_name>,                                                                                                                                    │
│   "args": <tool_args>                                                                                                                                     │
│ }                                                                                                                                                         │
│ </tool_call>                                                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                           │
│ For example:                                                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                           │
│ <tool_call>                                                                                                                                               │
